### Glass Effect Standards
- Use `backdrop-blur-lg` for primary glass surfaces
- Combine with `bg-white/10` or `bg-black/20` for depth
- Add `border border-white/20` for definition
- Use `rounded-2xl` for primary containers, `rounded-xl` for cards

